  "instructions": [
    "Cook the pancit canton noodles according to package instructions and set aside.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the vegetable oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced Persian cucumber and stir-fry until tender, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the confit tomato and stir-fry for another 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cooked noodles, floral soy sauce, salt, and black pepper, and stir-fry for 2 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Transfer the pancit canton to a serving platter and garnish with chopped scallions.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
